   CONGO-RWANDA (Abidjan, Ivory Coast) _ A pilot's account gives
the lie to the official Rwandan story of non-involvement in latest
fighting in the Democratic Republic of Congo. By Howard W. French.
</P>
<P>
   IRAQ-U.N. (Undated) _ The U.N. Special Commission suspends arms
inspections of new sites in Iraq after Baghdad's decision to halt
cooperation with U.N. arms inspectors. By Barbara Crossette.
</P>
