<P>
   REPUBS-POLITICS (Washington) _ Republicans go home for summer
with divisions as deep, though not as vocal, as last year's. Fault
lines between social conservatives and business conservatives get
deeper and mess up all kinds of legislation. By Alison Mitchell.
</P>
