   8/10 MOON PHASES -- 1 x 5/8 -- The phases of the moon.
</P>
<P>
   8/10 EXTENDED FORECAST -- 51p x 2 -- Four day forecast in two
maps.
</P>
<P>
   The New York Times News Service
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
