<HEADER>
A5483 &Cx1f; tad-z
b s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-MARTINEZ-ADVISORY-COX     08-09 0054
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-MARTINEZ-ADVISORY-COX </SLUG>

<TEXT>
<P>
   Atlanta Braves pitcher Dennis Martinez passes Juan Marichal's
all-time record to become the winningest Latin American pitcher in
Major League Baseball. Atlanta Journal-Constitution story to
follow.
</P>
<P>
   Story Filed By Cox Newspapers
</P>
